# String Manipulator 📝

Performs various operations on strings provided by the user.

## Features
- Converts strings to uppercase and lowercase
- Reverses strings
- Counts characters and words

## Technologies
- Python

## What I learned
- String methods
- User input handling
- Function creation

## Run the program
```bash
python string_manipulator.py
